==症狀==
此疾病屬於[[骨軟骨病|骨軟骨病]]，初始的病灶原發於軟骨之中，之後受損的軟骨會從關節上鬆脫，進而引起疼痛和[[發炎|發炎]]，這些軟骨碎片則被稱為關節內游動體（joint mice）<ref name="pmid10643956-patient information handout">{{cite journal|vauthors=Hixon AL, Gibbs LM|title=What Should I Know About Osteochondritis Dissecans?|journal=American Family Physician|volume=61|issue=1|page=158|date=January 2000|url=http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000101/20000101d.html|access-date=2020-01-08|archive-date=2011-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113031443/http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000101/20000101d.html}}</ref>。本病最常進犯膝關節，另也可能進犯踝關節和肘關節<ref name="pmid6807595"/>。

患者一開始會以運動相關疼痛表現，常見主訴包含疼痛、關節腫，運動時可能感覺會有不順暢感（locking）、絆住感（catching）、產生彈響（popping noises），或軟腳（buckling）。有時會以關節活動度縮小作為初始表現<ref name="pmid10643956">{{cite journal|vauthors=Hixon AL, Gibbs LM|title=Osteochondritis dissecans: a diagnosis not to miss|journal=American Family Physician|volume=61|issue=1|pages=151–6, 158|date=January 2000|pmid=10643956|url=http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000101/151.html|access-date=2020-01-08|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606043721/http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000101/151.html}}</ref>。第一期症狀通常在幾周內即會出現，第二期症狀大約會於一個月內出現，但若在此時未即時診斷出來，則病程會急遽惡化，病灶會從穩定的囊腫或裂縫，快速發展為不穩定的碎片。此時會出現類似[[扭傷|扭傷]]和{{tsl|en|strain (injury)|拉傷|}}的一些[[症狀|非特異性症狀]]，常延誤診斷<ref name="urlOCDofKNEE">{{cite web|url=http://www.eorthopod.com/osteochondritis-dissecans-of-the-knee/topic/68|title=Adolescent Osteochondritis Dissecans of the Knee|accessdate=2008-09-21|author=eOrthopod.com|publisher=Medical Multimedia Group, LLC|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001222250/http://www.eorthopod.com/osteochondritis-dissecans-of-the-knee/topic/68|archivedate=2014-10-01}}</ref>。

理學檢查一般可以發現關節積液、疼痛，和{{tsl|en|crepitus|關節摩擦音|}}。疼痛一開始會大面積的出現，但之後會逐漸縮小到一個特定的局部位置。剝脫性骨軟骨炎的症狀與許多常見疾病相同，例如急性骨軟骨骨折（acute osteochondral fracture）同樣也會造成關節壓痛，但急性骨軟骨骨折通常較容易脂肪性{{tsl|en|hemarthrosis|關節血腫|關節積血}}。剝脫性骨軟骨炎不會造成特別的病理性步態，但患者可能會刻意將小腿外旋，避免脛骨棘（tibial spine）遭到{{tsl|en|Medial condyle of femur|股骨內髁|}}外側面夾擊（impingement）<ref name="pmid8613454">{{cite journal|author1=Schenck RC Jr|author2=Goodnight JM|title=Osteochondritis dissecans|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|volume=78|issue=3|pages=439–56|date=1996-03-01|pmid=8613454|url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/content/full/78/3/439|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007082532/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/content/full/78/3/439|archivedate=2008-10-07|doi=10.2106/00004623-199603000-00018}}</ref>。

==病因==
{{see also|骨軟骨炎}}
剝脫性骨軟骨關節炎的成因迄今未明，相關的假說包含[[創傷|物理性因素]]、[[遺傳|基因遺傳]]、[[缺血|血液供應不足]]，以及股骨遠端骨骺板異常骨化等等<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Nonoperative Treatment of Osteochondritis Dissecans of the Knee|author=|url=https://www.sportsmed.theclinics.com/article/S0278-5919(13)00127-0/abstract|last=Wright|first=Rick W.|last2=Bogunovic|first2=Ljiljana|date=2014-04-01|journal=Clinics in Sports Medicine|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.csm.2013.11.003|others=|year=|volume=33|page=|pages=295–304|language=|issn=0278-5919|pmid=24698044|last3=Yang|first3=Justin S.}}</ref>。雖然本疾病被稱為「骨軟骨關節炎」，但組織學上缺乏發炎細胞參與，屬於一種非發炎性疾病。目前認為骨關節反覆性的{{tsl|en|microtrauma|微創傷|}}會導致硬骨的輕微磨損，進而影響軟骨下硬骨的血流供應，導致硬骨缺血或生長異常<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Pediatric Knee Osteochondritis Dissecans Lesions|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27637663?dopt=Abstract|last=Cruz|first=Aristides I.|last2=Shea|first2=Kevin G.|date=2016-10|journal=The Orthopedic Clinics of North America|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.ocl.2016.05.001|volume=47|pages=763–775|issn=1558-1373|pmid=27637663|last3=Ganley|first3=Theodore J.}}</ref>。

創傷比起缺血性骨壞死，更容易直接導致青少年罹患剝脫性骨軟骨炎<ref name=":0" /><ref name="pmid622473">{{cite journal|title=Radiological and pathological manifestations of osteochondritis dissecans of the distal femur. A study of 50 cases|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_radiology_1978-02_126_2/page/305|author=Milgram JW|date=February 1978|journal=Radiology|issue=2|doi=10.1148/126.2.305|volume=126|pages=305–311|pmid=622473}}</ref>。而在成人，[[内源|內源性]]或{{tsl|en|exogenous|外源性|}}的創傷亦常是造成剝脫性骨軟骨炎的主因，甚至創傷本身就可以單獨造成本疾病<ref name="Roberts 1961">{{cite journal|title=Book Reviews|author=Roberts N|url=http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/43-B/2/409.pdf|date=March 1961|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. British Volume|issue=2|volume=43|page=409|format=PDF|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061546/http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/43-B/2/409.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。青少年運動員發生[[重複使力傷害|重複使力傷害]]的發生率近年來逐年上升，這可能肇因於就醫頻率的增加<ref name="pmid18556892">{{cite journal |author=Powers R |title=An ice hockey player with an unusual elbow injury. Osteochondritis dissecans |journal=JAAPA |volume=21 |issue=5 |pages=62–3 |date=May 2008 |pmid=18556892 |doi= |url=}}</ref>。這更佐證剝脫性骨軟骨炎可能與運動及其相關損傷相關<ref name="pmid18556892" /><ref name="pmid16794036">{{cite journal|vauthors=Kocher MS, Tucker R, Ganley TJ, Flynn JM |title=Management of osteochondritis dissecans of the knee: current concepts review|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-sports-medicine_2006-07_34_7/page/1181 |journal=American Journal of Sports Medicine|volume=34|issue=7|pages=1181–91|date=July 2006|pmid=16794036|doi=10.1177/0363546506290127}}</ref>。從事體操、足球、籃球、袋棍球、足球、網球、壁球、籃球，及舉重等高衝擊性的活動，可能會使主要受壓關節（膝、踝、肘）發生剝脫性骨軟骨關節炎的機會增加<ref name="pmid10643956" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emedicine.com/sports/TOPIC51.HTM|title=Humeral Capitellum Osteochondritis Dissecans|accessdate=2008-11-16|last=Patel|first=S|author2=Fried GW|author3=Marone PJ|date=2008-08-06|work=[[EMedicine|eMedicine]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Medscape||Medscape}}|archive-date=2008-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207005344/http://www.emedicine.com/sports/topic51.htm}}</ref>。

最近的病例報告顯示剝脫性骨軟骨關節炎可能與遺傳相關<ref name="pmid18929205">{{cite journal|vauthors=Kenniston JA, Beredjiklian PK, Bozentka DJ |title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the capitellum in fraternal twins: case report|journal=Journal of Hand Surgery (American)|volume=33|issue=8|pages=1380–3 |date=October 2008|pmid=18929205|doi=10.1016/j.jhsa.2008.05.008}}</ref><ref name="pmid1428308">{{cite journal|vauthors=Livesley PJ, Milligan GF |title=Osteochondritis dissecans patellae. Is there a genetic predisposition?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_international-orthopaedics_1992-06_16_2/page/126 |journal=International Orthopaedics|volume=16|issue=2|pages=126–9|year=1992|pmid=1428308|doi=10.1007/BF00180201}}</ref><ref name="pmid13475409">{{cite journal|author=Tobin WJ|title=Familial osteochondritis dissecans with associated tibia vara|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|volume=39|issue=5|pages=1091–1105|date=October 1957|pmid=13475409|url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/39/5/1091.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-11-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318145633/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/39/5/1091.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-18|doi=10.2106/00004623-195739050-00010}}</ref>。有此類遺傳的家族可能有{{tsl|en|aggrecan|聚集蛋白聚醣|}}基因變化<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Emerging Genetic Basis of Osteochondritis Dissecans|author=|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0278591913001282|last=Bates|first=J. Tyler|last2=Jacobs|first2=John C.|date=2014-4|journal=Clinics in Sports Medicine|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.csm.2013.11.004|others=|year=|volume=33|page=|pages=199–220|language=|pmid=|last3=Shea|first3=Kevin G.|last4=Oxford|first4=Julia Thom|access-date=2020-01-08|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712032811/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0278591913001282}}</ref>。馬相關的研究也顯示可能有特定的遺傳缺陷<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Associations between Candidate Gene Markers at a Quantitative Trait Locus on Equine Chromosome 4 Responsible for Osteochondrosis Dissecans in Fetlock Joints of South German Coldblood Horses|author=|url=http://academic.oup.com/jhered/article/99/2/125/2188030/Associations-between-Candidate-Gene-Markers-at-a|last=Wittwer|first=Catherine|last2=Dierks|first2=Claudia|date=2008-04-01|journal=Journal of Heredity|issue=2|doi=10.1093/jhered/esm106|others=|year=|volume=99|page=|pages=125–129|language=|issn=1465-7333|pmid=|last3=Hamann|first3=Henning|last4=Distl|first4=Ottmar}}</ref>。

==病生理學==
[[File:Osteochondritis_dissecans_diagram.JPEG|thumb]]
剝脫性骨軟骨炎與磨損性的[[骨关节炎|退化性關節炎]]不同，後者屬於單純關節面的問題，而前者則是軟骨下面的硬骨問題，可能進而導致軟骨的損傷。如果沒有及時治療，剝脫性骨軟骨關節炎可能會引致關節不平衡以及不正常磨損，進而導致退化性關節炎<ref name="pmid18500061">{{cite journal|vauthors=Detterline AJ, Goldstein JL, Rue JP, ((Bach BR Jr)) |title=Evaluation and treatment of osteochondritis dissecans lesions of the knee|journal=Journal of Knee Surgery|volume=21|issue=2|pages=106–15|year=2008|pmid=18500061}}</ref>。剝脫性骨軟骨炎會發生時，硬骨或軟骨會從骨骼末端鬆離，通常是因為缺乏血液供應或{{tsl|en|Trabecular bone|海綿骨|}}脫鈣導致。鬆解的碎片可能會留在原地或是到處滑移，導致[[关节|關節]]僵硬且不穩定。本疾病可能發生於在身上所有的關節<ref name="pmid17980849">{{cite journal|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the talus involving the subtalar joint: a case report|journal=Journal of Foot and Ankle Surgery|issue=6|doi=10.1053/j.jfas.2007.06.005|year=2007|volume=46|pages=488–92|pmid=17980849|vauthors=Kadakia AP, Sarkar J}}</ref>，人類最常發病的位置包含膝關節<ref name="pmid6807595">{{cite journal|vauthors=Clanton TO, DeLee JC |title=Osteochondritis dissecans. History, pathophysiology and current treatment concepts|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_clinical-orthopaedics-and-related-research_1982-07_167/page/50 |journal=Clinical Orthopaedics and Related Research|volume=167 |pages=50–64|date=July 1982|pmid=6807595|issue=167|doi=10.1097/00003086-198207000-00009}}</ref>、踝關節、肘關節等<ref name="pmid17980849" />。

骨骼尚未成熟的個體身上，[[骺板|骨骺板]]的血流供應較充足，因此{{tsl|en|osteogenesis|硬骨生成|硬骨}}及{{tsl|en|chondrogenesis|軟骨生成|軟骨}}的生長較為旺盛。當骨骺板的血流供應受到阻礙時，會阻滯了{{tsl|en|osteocytes|硬骨細胞|}}和[[软骨细胞|軟骨細胞]]的生長，以及各種程度的壞死。此狀況也會導致軟骨不規則骨化，導致軟骨下{{tsl|en|avascular necrosis|缺血性壞死|}}，進而導致剝脫性骨關節炎<ref name="topic57webmd">{{cite web|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/89718-overview|title=Knee Osteochondritis Dissecans|accessdate=2008-10-02|vauthors=Jacobs B, Ertl JP, Kovacs G, Jacobs JA|work=eMedicine|publisher=Medscape|archive-date=2021-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718121457/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/89718-overview}}</ref>。

創傷後剝脫性骨關節炎可以分為四期：第一期為{{tsl|en|revascularization|再血管化|}}及再生肉芽組織生成；第二期時壞死的碎片會出現被吸收的現象；第三期的骨小樑間隙會出現類骨質（osteoid）沉積的現象；第四期開始出現新骨骼重塑的情形。若在再血管化階段受到阻滯，則剝脫性骨軟骨炎病灶可能生成，引致關節面失去平整性，進而惡化關節炎的情形<ref name="topic57webmd"/>。

==診斷==
診斷可透過[[X射线|X光]]、[[X射线计算机断层成像|電腦斷層]]，或[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]（MRI）進行。影像學可以幫助定位軟骨下區域壞死的位置，也能夠協助看到游離體的產生與否<ref name="pmid12591666">{{cite journal|vauthors=Boutin RD, Januario JA, Newberg AH, Gundry CR, Newman JS|title=MR imaging features of osteochondritis dissecans of the femoral sulcus|journal=American Journal of Roentgenology|volume=180|issue=3|pages=641–5|date=March 2003|pmid=12591666|url=http://www.ajronline.org/cgi/reprint/180/3/641.pdf|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090318145650/http://www.ajronline.org/cgi/reprint/180/3/641.pdf|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2009-03-18|format=PDF|doi=10.2214/ajr.180.3.1800641}}</ref>。偶爾也可能會透過{{tsl|en|bone scan|骨骼掃描|}}等[[核医学|核子醫學]]技術來評估關節內軟骨的剝離程度<ref name="Mesgarzadeh">{{cite journal|vauthors=Mesgarzadeh M, Sapega AA, Bonakdarpour A, Revesz G, Moyer RA, Maurer AH, Alburger PD|title=Osteochondritis dissecans: analysis of mechanical stability with radiography, scintigraphy, and MR imaging|journal=Radiology|volume=165|issue=3|pages=775–80|date=1987-12-01|pmid=3685359|url=http://radiology.rsnajnls.org/cgi/reprint/165/3/775|doi=10.1148/radiology.165.3.3685359|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2009-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604101601/http://radiology.rsnajnls.org/cgi/reprint/165/3/775}}</ref>。

===理學檢查===
檢查者一開始常會先評估患者的{{tsl|en|Gait (human)|步態 (人類)|步態}}。在膝關節受到進犯的患者，患者的小腿常會些微向外旋轉，以避免[[胫骨|脛骨]]棘受到{{tsl|en|Medial condyle of femur|股骨內髁|股骨內髁}}外側面的夾擊<ref name="pmid8613454"/>。因此對於股骨髁受到進犯的患者，可透過{{tsl|en|Wilson test|威爾森氏測試|}}（Wilson test）重現夾擊的情形<ref name="pmid6022357">{{cite journal|title=A diagnostic sign in osteochondritis dissecans of the knee|author=Wilson JN|url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/49/3/477.pdf|date=April 1967|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|issue=3|doi=10.2106/00004623-196749030-00006|volume=49|pages=477–80|format=PDF|pmid=6022357|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061547/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/49/3/477.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。施測者先請患者膝關節成90度，之後將小腿內旋後伸直，若伸展至150度時會感覺疼痛，且在將小腿外旋後症狀緩解，則檢查呈陽性<ref name="pmid12975201">{{cite journal|vauthors=Conrad JM, Stanitski CL |title=Osteochondritis dissecans: Wilson's sign revisited|journal=Am J Sports Med|volume=31|issue=5 |pages=777–8|year=2003|pmid=12975201}}</ref>。此外患者的[[股四頭肌|股四頭肌]]功能也可能會有有無力的情形<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the knee: Diagnosis and treatment|author=|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S2255497115300033|last=Mestriner|first=Luiz Aurélio|date=2012-09|journal=Revista Brasileira de Ortopedia (English Edition)|issue=5|doi=10.1016/S2255-4971(15)30003-3|others=|year=|volume=47|page=|pages=553–562|language=en|pmc=PMC4799442|pmid=27047865|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723222649/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S2255497115300033}}</ref>。

膝關節理學檢查也可能可以看到關節腔積水以及出現{{tsl|en|crepitus|關節摩擦音|}}。症狀上可能會感覺到局部或廣泛性疼痛，以及關節活動度下降。若出現軟骨游離體的患者，活動上可能會出現卡卡的感覺，或產生絆住感<ref name="cooperwebmd" />。

===診斷影像學===
兒童期患者的關節X光可能可以看到骨骺板出現不規則[[成骨作用|骨化]]的情形；年長患者則可能在病灶處出現{{tsl|en|Osteosclerosis|骨硬化|}}病灶，並在病灶處及骨骺之間形成骨密度較低的區域。病灶的原發部位以及膝關節的屈曲程度，可以進行側面膝關節X光以輔助定位<ref name="pmid852179">{{cite journal|author=Harding WG 3rd.|title=Diagnosis of osteochondritis dissecans of the femoral condyles: the value of the lateral x-ray view|journal=Clinical Orthopaedics and Related Research|volume=123|pages=25–6|date=March–April 1977|pmid=852179|issue=123|doi=10.1097/00003086-197703000-00009}}</ref>。

[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]（MRI）在病灶的分期上相當有用，可以評估膝關節表面的完整性。此外，有一些正常的骨質增生變異，在X光下會相當類似剝脫性骨軟骨炎病灶，但在MRI下，真正的病灶會呈現不規則的硬骨及軟骨水腫。此外，MRI也可以提供硬骨及軟組織的相關資訊，例如是否有骨折、水腫、液體介面、{{tsl|en|Articular cartilage damage|關節軟骨損傷|關節面}}完整性，或有游離體產生等問題<ref name="pmid2009106">{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/0749-8063(91)90087-E|vauthors=De Smet AA, Fisher DR, Graf BK, Lange RH |title=Characterizing osteochondral lesions by magnetic resonance imaging|journal=Arthroscopy|volume=7|issue=1|pages=101–4|year=1991|pmid=2009106 }}</ref><ref name="pmid2117355">{{cite journal |vauthors=De Smet AA, Fisher DR, Graf BK, Lange RH |title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the knee: value of MR imaging in determining lesion stability and the presence of articular cartilage defects |journal=AJR Am J Roentgenol |volume=155 |issue=3 |pages=549–53 |date=September 1990 |pmid=2117355 |doi= 10.2214/ajr.155.3.2117355|url=}}</ref>。活躍病灶在高T2權重影像可以看到軟骨及下方硬骨碎裂的情形<ref name="pmid12591666"/><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Prognosis for Improvement in Comfort and Function After the Ream-and-Run Arthroplasty for Glenohumeral Arthritis: An Analysis of 176 Consecutive Cases|url=https://journals.lww.com/jbjsjournal/Abstract/2012/07180/The_Prognosis_for_Improvement_in_Comfort_and.16.aspx|last=Gilmer|first=Brian B.|last2=Comstock|first2=Bryan A.|date=2012-07-18|journal=JBJS|issue=14|doi=10.2106/JBJS.K.00486|volume=94|pages=e102|language=en-US|issn=0021-9355|last3=Jette|first3=Jocelyn L.|last4=Warme|first4=Winston J.|last5=Jackins|first5=Sarah E.|last6=Matsen|first6=Frederick A. III|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716111855/https://journals.lww.com/jbjsjournal/Abstract/2012/07180/The_Prognosis_for_Improvement_in_Comfort_and.16.aspx}}</ref>。與關節X光片相比，MRI影像更加吻合[[关节镜|關節鏡]]的檢查結果<ref name="pmid2117355"/>。

[[X射线计算机断层成像|電腦斷層]]（CT）與[[鎝-99m|鎝-99m]]（Tc-99m）{{tsl|en|bone scan|骨骼掃描|}}有時也會用於追蹤後續治療效果。CT和MRI可以協助病灶的定位，以及判讀病灶的大小<ref name="pmid11044029">{{cite journal|vauthors=Bui-Mansfield LT, Kline M, Chew FS, Rogers LF, Lenchik L|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the tibial plafond: imaging characteristics and a review of the literature|journal=American Journal of Roentgenology|volume=175|issue=5|pages=1305–8|date=2000-11-01|pmid=11044029|url=http://www.ajronline.org/cgi/content/full/175/5/1305|doi=10.2214/ajr.175.5.1751305|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2011-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517204641/http://www.ajronline.org/cgi/content/full/175/5/1305}}</ref>；骨骼掃描則可以偵測局部血流以及骨骼代謝活躍程度<ref name="pmid6638247">{{cite journal|vauthors=Cahill BR, Berg BC |title=99m-Technetium phosphate compound joint scintigraphy in the management of juvenile osteochondritis dissecans of the femoral condyles|journal=American Journal of Sports Medicine|volume=11|issue=5|pages=329–35|year=1983|pmid=6638247|doi=10.1177/036354658301100509}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eorthopod.com/public/files/Adolescent_Osteochondritis_Dissecans_of_the_Elbow.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027030205/http://www.eorthopod.com/public/files/Adolescent_Osteochondritis_Dissecans_of_the_Elbow.pdf|archivedate=2007-10-27|title=Adolescent Osteochondritis Dissecans of the Elbow|accessdate=2008-10-02|author=eOrthopod.com|format=PDF|publisher=Medical Multimedia Group, LLC}}</ref>。<gallery>
