===分類===
剝脫性骨軟骨炎可透過其疾病的進程進行分期，目前有兩套主流的分類系統：一個是透過MRI影像進行分期<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Management of Osteochondritis Dissecans Lesions of the Knee, Elbow and Ankle|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28577707/|last=Bauer|first=Kathryn L.|last2=Polousky|first2=John D.|date=2017-07|journal=Clinics in Sports Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.csm.2017.02.005|volume=36|pages=469–487|issn=1556-228X|pmid=28577707|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718101552/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28577707/}}</ref>，另一個則是透過[[关节镜|關節鏡]]檢查進行分期<ref name="pmid10643956"/>。其中關節鏡是分類的黃金標準，目前最為廣泛使用的分期標準為國際軟骨修復學會（International Cartilage Repair Society）提出的ICRS分期系統<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Magnetic Resonance Imaging of Osteochondritis Dissecans: Validation Study for the ICRS Classification System|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S107663321600101X|last=Ellermann|first=Jutta M.|last2=Donald|first2=Bryan|date=2016-06-01|journal=Academic Radiology|issue=6|doi=10.1016/j.acra.2016.01.015|volume=23|pages=724–729|language=en|issn=1076-6332|last3=Rohr|first3=Sara|last4=Takahashi|first4=Takashi|last5=Tompkins|first5=Marc|last6=Nelson|first6=Bradley|last7=Crawford|first7=Amanda|last8=Rud|first8=Christopher|last9=Macalena|first9=Jeffrey}}</ref>。現行MRI分期系統中，ICRS的MRI分期系統是論文中最常使用的分期系統<ref name="pmid10887249">{{cite journal|vauthors=Takahara M, Ogino T, Takagi M, Tsuchida H, Orui H, Nambu T|title=Natural progression of osteochondritis dissecans of the humeral capitellum: initial observations|journal=Radiology|volume=216|issue=1|pages=207–12|date=2000-07-01|pmid=10887249|url=http://radiology.rsnajnls.org/cgi/content/full/216/1/207?maxtoshow=&HITS=10&hits=10&RESULTFORMAT=1&andorexacttitle=and&titleabstract=osteochondritis+dissecans&andorexacttitleabs=and&andorexactfulltext=and&searchid=1&FIRSTINDEX=0&sortspec=relevance&resourcetype=HWCIT|doi=10.1148/radiology.216.1.r00jl29207|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2009-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604102416/http://radiology.rsnajnls.org/cgi/content/full/216/1/207?maxtoshow=&HITS=10&hits=10&RESULTFORMAT=1&andorexacttitle=and&titleabstract=osteochondritis+dissecans&andorexacttitleabs=and&andorexactfulltext=and&searchid=1&FIRSTINDEX=0&sortspec=relevance&resourcetype=HWCIT}}</ref>，但有些研究顯示MRI與關節鏡之間的對應關係並不密切<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Magnetic Resonance Imaging of Osteochondritis Dissecans: Validation Study for the ICRS Classification System|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26976624/|last=Ellermann|first=Jutta M.|last2=Donald|first2=Bryan|date=06 2016|journal=Academic Radiology|issue=6|doi=10.1016/j.acra.2016.01.015|volume=23|pages=724–729|issn=1878-4046|pmid=26976624|last3=Rohr|first3=Sara|last4=Takahashi|first4=Takashi|last5=Tompkins|first5=Marc|last6=Nelson|first6=Bradley|last7=Crawford|first7=Amanda|last8=Rud|first8=Christopher|last9=Macalena|first9=Jeffrey|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716090438/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26976624/}}</ref>。MRI分期分為四期，其中一、二期為穩定病灶，三、四期則為不穩定病灶。到第三、四期時，可以在碎片與骨骼之間看到{{tsl|en|synovial fluid|關節滑液|}}<ref name=":1" />。

