現行針對全層病灶的治療包含關節鏡導引骨鑽孔術（arthroscopic drilling）、關節面磨平術（abrasion），以及微骨折手術（microfracturing）。

1946年，芒努松（Magnusson）首創使用[[骨髓|骨髓]]幹細胞搭配[[清創手術|清創手術]]治療病灶的方法，但這些幹細胞通常會分化為[[纤维软骨|纖維軟骨]]，較少分化為[[透明软骨|透明軟骨]]。由於纖維軟骨相對透明軟骨的韌性及對於磨損的耐受性較差，因此術後必須保護6到12個月。該術式對於小型病灶有效，對於大型病灶來說效果則會漸漸消失<ref name="pmid9850792">{{cite journal |vauthors=Mandelbaum BR, Browne JE, Fu F, etal |title=Articular cartilage lesions of the knee|journal=American Journal of Sports Medicine|volume=26|issue=6|pages=853–61|year=1998|pmid=9850792}}</ref>。有鑑於再生的纖維軟骨結構較為脆弱，後來發展出來的技術開始著重於移植透明軟骨，或促進病灶處的透明軟骨增生。其中一種方法就是自體軟骨細胞移植術（autologous chondrocyte implantation，ACI），這種方法對於年輕患者股骨的單發性大型病灶有效。在此術式中，醫師會使用關節鏡從{{tsl|en|Intercondylar fossa of femur|股骨髁間窩|髁間窩}}的關節面取出部分軟骨，並植入病灶下面的[[骨膜|骨膜]]處。目前的研究顯示，ACI手術在減少水腫及疼痛方面在臨床上具有良好的療效<ref name="pmid8078550">{{cite journal|vauthors=Brittberg M, Lindahl A, Nilsson A, Ohlsson C, Isaksson O, Peterson L|title=Treatment of deep cartilage defects in the knee with autologous chondrocyte transplantation|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|volume=331|issue=14|pages=889–95|date=October 1994|pmid=8078550|url=http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/331/14/889|accessdate=2008-09-17|doi=10.1056/NEJM199410063311401|archive-date=2009-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090805175114/http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/331/14/889}}</ref><ref name="pmid10818982">{{cite journal|vauthors=Peterson L, Minas T, Brittberg M, Nilsson A, Sjögren-Jansson E, Lindahl A |title=Two to Nine-year outcome after autologous chondrocyte transplantation of the knee|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_clinical-orthopaedics-and-related-research_2000-05_374/page/212 |journal=Clinical Orthopaedics and Related Research|issue=374|pages=212–34|date=May 2000|pmid=10818982|doi=10.1097/00003086-200005000-00020|volume=374}}</ref>。有些醫師利用骨膜或骨髓的多能性幹細胞取代，同樣也顯示出軟骨及軟骨下硬骨再生的能力<ref name="pmid9875939">{{cite journal|author=O'Driscoll SW|title=The healing and regeneration of articular cartilage|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|volume=80|issue=12|pages=1795–1812|date=December 1998|pmid=9875939|url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/80/12/1795.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061541/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/80/12/1795.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29}}</ref>。

與OATS手術相似的是，關節鏡導引關節軟骨移植手術花費低廉，且針對第四期病灶效果持久。且植體來自於不須承重的髁間窩，可以舒緩疼痛、修復受傷組織，並恢復關節功能<ref name="pmid16517314">{{cite journal |vauthors=Stone KR, Walgenbach AW, Freyer A, Turek TJ, Speer DP |title=Articular cartilage paste grafting to full-thickness articular cartilage knee joint lesions: a 2- to 12-year follow-up |journal=Arthroscopy |volume=22 |issue=3 |pages=291–9 |date=March 2006 |pmid=16517314 |doi=10.1016/j.arthro.2005.12.051}}</ref>。

====不穩定病灶====
不穩定病灶的固定，有時可以用不鏽鋼或生物可吸收材質製造的埋頭加壓骨釘或{{tsl|en|Timothy Herbert|提摩西·赫伯特|赫伯特骨釘}}（Herbert screw）進行固定<ref name="pmid17337729">{{cite journal |vauthors=Kocher MS, Czarnecki JJ, Andersen JS, Micheli LJ |title=Internal fixation of juvenile osteochondritis dissecans lesions of the knee |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-sports-medicine_2007-05_35_5/page/712 |journal=American Journal of Sports Medicine |volume=35 |issue=5 |pages=712–8 |date=May 2007 |pmid=17337729 |doi=10.1177/0363546506296608}}</ref>。若有看到游離體，可同時進行移除。ACI手術一般適用於骨骼成熟且病灶較大的病人身上。

====復健====
連續性被動運動（Continuous passive motion，CPM）常用於促進全層病灶患者術後關節面的修復。研究發現CPM在兔子身上，可以促進直徑3毫米以下的病灶修復<ref name="pmid7440603">{{cite journal |vauthors=Salter RB, Simmonds DF, Malcolm BW, Rumble EJ, MacMichael D, Clements ND |title=The biological effect of continuous passive motion on the healing of full-thickness defects in articular cartilage. An experimental investigation in the rabbit |journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery |volume=62 |issue=8 |pages=1232–51 |date=December 1980 |pmid=7440603 |url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/62/8/1232.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318145705/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/62/8/1232.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-18 }}</ref>。在人類身上，亦有研究指出每天6小時，持續八周的療程具有臨床效益<ref name="pmid8590122">{{cite journal |vauthors=Rodrigo JJ, Steadman JR, Syftestad G, Benton H, Silliman J |title=Effects of human knee synovial fluid on chondrogenesis in vitro |journal=American Journal of Knee Surgery |volume=8 |issue=4 |pages=124–9 |year=1995|pmid=8590122}}</ref>。

制定復健計畫時，需同時保護受損的關節面及軟骨下硬骨，同時保持強度和運動範圍。術後通常需要[[鴉片類藥物|鴉片類]][[镇痛药|鎮痛藥]]及[[非甾体抗炎药|非甾體抗炎藥]]（NSAID）來控制疼痛，發言和腫脹<ref>{{cite web|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/89718-treatment|title=Knee Osteochondritis dissecans: treatment & medication|accessdate=2009-02-14|vauthors=Jacobs B, Ertl JP, Kovacs G, Jacobs JA|date=2006-07-28|work=eMedicine|publisher=Medscape|archive-date=2021-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718102004/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/89718-treatment}}</ref>。在術後或固定期（immobilization period）間，鼓勵直腿抬高（straight leg raising）和其他[[等長運動|等長運動]]。固定期結束後，通常會立即進行六到八週的居家或正規[[物理治療|物理治療]]計劃。可執行的活動包含伸展運動、漸進式肌力訓練，以及針對功能或運動的訓練。在此期間，建議患者避免跑步和跳躍，但應允許他們進行影響較小的活動，例如散步或游泳。 如果患者在軟骨穩定之前，進行超過負荷活動量，常會在蹲踞或跳躍等過程中出現疼痛的症狀<ref name="orthogateKNEEOCD">{{cite web |url=http://www.orthogate.org/index2.php?option=com_content&do_pdf=1&id=185 |title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the knee |accessdate=2008-11-16 |date=2006-07-28 |format=PDF |publisher=Orthogate |archive-date=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701024800/http://www.orthogate.org/index2.php?option=com_content&do_pdf=1&id=185 }}</ref>。

==預後==
預後的影響因子包含治療方式、年紀、進犯的關節、病灶分期等等，但最關鍵的因子為生長板的狀態<ref name="cooperwebmd">{{cite web|url=http://www.emedicine.com/orthoped/topic639.htm|title=Definition of osteochondritis dissecans|accessdate=2008-09-18|vauthors=Cooper G, Russell W|work=eMedicine|publisher=Medscape|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201155435/http://www.emedicine.com/orthoped/topic639.htm}}</ref>。也因此，剝脫性骨軟骨炎可透過骨骼成熟度分為兩種主要形式。幼年型（juvenile form）通常發生於5至15歲的兒童身上，病灶常發生於未癒合的生長板上<ref>{{Cite book|vauthors=Fleisher GR, Ludwig S, Henretig FM, Ruddy RM, Silverman BK |year=2005|title=Textbook of Pediatric Emergency Medicine|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=0-7817-5074-1|url=https://books.google.com/?id=oA7qSOvYZxUC&pg=RA2-PA1703&lpg=RA2-PA1703&dq=free+ebook+osteochondritis|page=1703}}</ref>；成年型（adult form）則通常發生於16至50歲的族群，但目前並不知道這些患者是在成年後才發病，還是在幼年期未及時診斷的幼年型患者<ref>{{Cite book|vauthors=Simon RR, Sherman SC, Koenigsknecht SJ |year=2006|title=Emergency Orthopedics: The Extremities|publisher=McGraw-Hill Professional|isbn=0-07-144831-4|url=https://books.google.com/?id=nMXRDsufkMwC&pg=PA254&dq=osteochondritis+dissecans|page=254}}</ref>。

在生長板未癒合的青少年中，穩定型病灶的預後普遍良好（第一、二期），在保守治療下有50%的機率會痊癒<ref name="pmid10795030">{{cite journal|author=Cahill BR|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the knee: Treatment of juvenile and adult forms|journal=Journal of the American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons|volume=3|issue=4|pages=237–47|date=July 1995|pmid=10795030}}</ref>。這可能是因為青少年的骨質重塑機能較佳，意即其清除死亡骨骼，及新生骨骼的能力較強。且未癒合的生長板用有較多的[[間充質幹細胞|間質幹細胞]]，這些幹細胞之後可以分化為軟骨或硬骨，因而可以提供受損關節修復所需的幹細胞<ref name="Cartilage+GrowthPlates">{{cite book |author=Bogin B|title=Patterns of Human Growth|url=https://books.google.com/?id=ScfPjwF3BngC|accessdate=2009-02-20|edition=2|date=January 2008|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=0-521-56438-7|page=102|chapter=Mammalian Growth|chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=ScfPjwF3BngC&pg=PA102&lpg=PA102&dq=growth+plates+bone+remodeling&source=web&ots=gGxVx5XMbV&sig=KvWHnkgb5y7IktTLmoCcHNlqIF8&hl=en&ei=xCefSc-cGY-EtgeWjJz_DA&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=3&ct=result#PPA101,M1}}</ref>。大型、不穩定，或全層病灶（第三、四期），或是在骨骼發育成熟後才發生的病灶通常預後較差，保守治療的效果普遍不佳，通常需要手術介入<ref name="pmid2722949" /><ref name="pmid17680233">{{cite journal|vauthors=Lützner J, Mettelsiefen J, Günther KP, Thielemann F |title=Treatment of osteochondritis dissecans of the knee joint|language=de|journal=Der Orthopäde|volume=36|issue=9|pages=871–9; quiz 880|date=September 2007|pmid=17680233|doi=10.1007/s00132-007-1130-3}}</ref>。

==流行病學==
剝脫性骨軟骨炎相對來說算罕見疾病，大約每年每10萬人有15至30例<ref name="pmid9012566">{{cite journal|vauthors=Obedian RS, Grelsamer RP |title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the distal femur and patella|journal=Clinical Journal of Sport Medicine|volume=16|issue=1|pages=157–74|date=January 1997|pmid=9012566|doi=10.1016/S0278-5919(05)70012-0}}</ref>。有報告分析25,124例膝關節鏡報告，指出該疾病造成約2%的關節軟骨缺損<ref name="pmid17428666">{{cite journal|vauthors=Widuchowski W, Widuchowski J, Trzaska T |title=Articular cartilage defects: study of 25,124 knee arthroscopies |journal=The Knee|volume=14|issue=3|pages=177–82|date=June 2007|pmid=17428666|doi=10.1016/j.knee.2007.02.001}}</ref>。儘管如此，剝脫性骨軟骨炎仍然是青少年關節疼痛的重要病因。幼年型的疾病主要發生於5至15歲之間，且男性發生率又較女性為高，男女患者比大約介於2:1至3:1之間<ref name="pmid6807595" /><ref name="KonigNOPMID">{{cite journal|author=Nagura S|title=The so-called osteochondritis dissecans of Konig|journal=Clinical Orthopaedics and Related Research|volume=18|pages=100–121|year=1960}}</ref>。然而隨著女性和青少年在運動中益發活躍，女性患者以及幼年型的病例量也節節上升<ref name="pmid8917149">{{cite journal |vauthors=Williamson LR, Albright JP |title=Bilateral osteochondritis dissecans of the elbow in a female pitcher|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-family-practice_1996-11_43_5/page/489 |journal=Journal of Family Practice|volume=43|issue=5|pages=489–93|date=November 1996|pmid=8917149}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Nonoperative treatment of osteochondritis dissecans of the knee|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24698044?dopt=Abstract|last=Yang|first=Justin S.|last2=Bogunovic|first2=Ljiljana|date=2014-4|journal=Clinics in Sports Medicine|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.csm.2013.11.003|volume=33|pages=295–304|issn=1556-228X|pmid=24698044|last3=Wright|first3=Rick W.}}</ref>。成年型則主要發生於16至50之間<ref name="pmid2722949">{{cite journal|vauthors=Bradley J, Dandy DJ|title=Osteochondritis dissecans and other lesions of the femoral condyles|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. British Volume|volume=71|issue=3|pages=518–22|date=May 1989|pmid=2722949|url=http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/71-B/3/518.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061543/http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/71-B/3/518.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29}}</ref>。

在發生部位中，最常見的是膝關節的{{tsl|en|Medial condyle of femur|股骨內髁|}}，約佔膝關節病例的75–85%，並佔總病例的75%<ref name="pmid6807595" /><ref name="pmid6501330">{{cite journal|vauthors=Hughston JC, Hergenroeder PT, Courtenay BG|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the femoral condyles|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|volume=66|issue=9|pages=1340–8|date=December 1984|pmid=6501330|url=http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/66/9/1340.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061544/http://www.ejbjs.org/cgi/reprint/66/9/1340.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29|doi=10.2106/00004623-198466090-00003}}</ref><ref name="pmid5562371">{{cite journal|author=Aichroth P|title=Osteochondritis dissecans of the knee. A clinical survey|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. British Volume|volume=53|issue=3|pages=440–7|date=August 1971|pmid=5562371|url=http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/53-B/3/440.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029061544/http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/53-B/3/440.pdf|archivedate=2008-10-29}}</ref><ref name="pmid1015263">{{cite journal|author=Lindén B |title=The incidence of osteochondritis dissecans in the condyles of the femur|journal=Acta Orthopaedica Scandinavica|volume=47|issue=6|pages=664–7|date=December 1976|pmid=1015263|doi=10.3109/17453677608988756}}</ref>。肘關節（特別是{{tsl|en|capitulum of the humerus|肱骨小頭|}}）是第二常遭到進犯的關節，約佔總病例的6%左右。踝關節的[[距骨|距骨圓頂]]約佔總病例的4%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emedicine.com/orthoped/topic639.htm|title=Osteochondritis Dissecans|accessdate=2008-11-16|vauthors=Cooper G, Warren R|date=2008-05-15|work=eMedicine|publisher=Medscape|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201155435/http://www.emedicine.com/orthoped/topic639.htm}}</ref>。其他較罕見的發生部位包含[[髌骨|髕骨]]、[[脊椎骨|脊椎骨]]、股骨頭，以及肩胛骨的{{tsl|en|glenoid|肩關節盂|}}等等<ref name="pmid7803070">{{cite journal|vauthors=Tuite MJ, DeSmet AA |title=MRI of selected sports injuries: muscle tears, groin pain, and osteochondritis dissecans|journal=Seminars in Ultrasound, CT and MRI|volume=15|issue=5|pages=318–40|date=October 1994|pmid=7803070|doi=10.1016/S0887-2171(05)80002-2}}</ref>。

==歷史==
1738年，{{tsl|en|Alexander Monro (primus)|亞歷山大·門羅·普里默斯|}}首次描述了此一疾病<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Medical Essays and Observations |title=Part of the cartilage of the joint separated and ossified|author=Munro A|year=1738 |volume=4|page=19}} cited in {{cite journal |author=Burns RC |date=September 1939 |title=OSTEOCHONDRITIS DISSECANS |journal=CMAJ |volume=41 |issue=3 |pages=232–5 |pmc=537458 |pmid=20321457}}</ref>。1870年，{{tsl|en|James Paget|詹姆斯·柏哲德|}}首次描述此一疾病的病程。1887年，{{tsl|en|Franz König (surgeon)|弗朗茲·寇尼希 (外科醫師)|弗朗茲·寇尼希}}發表了一篇相關論文，並描述游離體的存在<ref name="pmid1868560">{{cite journal|author=Garrett JC|title=Osteochondritis dissecans|journal=Clinical Journal of Sport Medicine|volume=10|issue=3|pages=569–93|date=July 1991|pmid=1868560}}</ref>。在此篇論文中，寇尼希做出以下結論：<ref name="konig">{{cite journal|author=König F|title=Uber freie Korper in den gelenken|journal=Deutsche Zeitschrift für Chirurgie|volume=27|issue=1–2|pages=90–109|date=December 1888|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/m57696053j598h56/fulltext.pdf?page=1|language=de|doi=10.1007/BF02792135|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423235615/http://www.springerlink.com/content/m57696053j598h56/fulltext.pdf?page=1}}</ref>
# 要造成關節面崩落的創傷當屬嚴重創傷。
#較輕微的創傷可能造成骨骼挫傷，導致局部壞死，進而引發軟骨脫落。
# 在某些病例中，沒有明顯的創傷史，可能有其他因素導致軟骨自發性脫離。
在此論文中，他將該疾病命名為「剝脫性骨軟骨炎」（osteochondritis dissecans）<ref name="pmid3316236">{{cite journal|author=Barrie HJ|title=Osteochondritis dissecans 1887–1987. A centennial look at König's memorable phrase|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. British Volume|volume=69|issue=5|pages=693–5|date=November 1987|pmid=3316236|url=http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/69-B/5/693.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318145633/http://www.jbjs.org.uk/cgi/reprint/69-B/5/693.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-18}}</ref>，將其描述為一種膝關節軟骨下硬骨發炎的過程，進而導致股骨髁軟骨鬆脫的情形。1922年，卡匹斯（Kappis）在踝關節報導了此病例<ref name="kappis">{{cite journal|author=Kappis M|title=Weitere beitrage zur traumatisch-mechanischen entstehung der "spontanen" knorpela biosungen|journal=Deutsche Zeitschrift für Chirurgie |volume=171|pages=13–29|year=1922|language=de|doi=10.1007/BF02812921}}</ref>。後來伯恩特（Berndt）和哈替（Harty）在回顧了多篇描述[[距骨|距骨]]軟骨骨折的文獻後，提出了距骨剝脫性骨軟骨炎的分類系統（staging of osteochondral lesions of the talus，OLTs）<ref name="pmid15173311">{{cite journal|vauthors=Berndt AL, Harty M |title=Transchondral fractures (osteochondritis dissecans) of the talus|journal=Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume|volume=86|issue=6|page=1336|date=June 2004|pmid=15173311|doi=10.2106/00004623-200406000-00032}}</ref>。此論文拓展了剝脫性骨軟骨炎的描述範圍，使包含膝關節、髖關節、肘關節，以及{{tsl|en|Metatarsophalangeal articulations|蹠趾關節|}}的相似疾病都納入此一疾病的範疇中<ref>{{Cite book|author=Morrey BF|year=2000|title=The Elbow and Its Disorders|url=https://archive.org/details/elbowitsdisorder0000unse_j3p5|place=Philadelphia, PA|publisher= W.B. Saunders|isbn=0-7216-7752-5|pages=[https://archive.org/details/elbowitsdisorder0000unse_j3p5/page/250 250]–60}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|vauthors=Walzer J, Pappas AM |year=1995|title=Upper Extremity Injuries in the Athlete|url=https://archive.org/details/upperextremityin0000unse_h0s4 |location=Edinburgh, UK|publisher=Churchill Livingstone|isbn=0-443-08836-5|page=[https://archive.org/details/upperextremityin0000unse_h0s4/page/132 132]}}</ref>。

